	"classname" "asw_objective_triggered"
	"objectivedescription1" "Syntek have a serious problem they have an important director stuck in the city. He is held up in a Syntek building, completely over run by the swarm. You have to walk him out of there."
	"objectivedescription2" "I'm sure you know already but Omega city is infested by the swarm. Its population is all but dead except a few lucky people who escaped in time."
	"objectivedescription3" "Don't expect to have a peaceful time and let me stress this, Syntek do not want this guy to be killed so don't let it happen marines! I trust you will get the job done."
	"objectiveimage" "rd_Omegacity_objreach"
	"objectivemarkername" "path_blocked_obj_marker"
	"objectivetitle" "Head towards the Syntek building"
	"targetname" "path_blocked_obj"
	"Visible" "1"
	connections
	{
		"OnObjectiveComplete" "alternativepath_objSetVisible-10-1"
	}
	"origin" "-1713 -7618 328"
	editor
	{
